OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1782397118
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 10 Jul to Fri 24 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure patterns are looking
OL,7,Fslightly more likely than low pressure
OL,8,Fpatterns during the early part of this
OL,9,Fperiod, meaning a greater chance of
OL,10,Fsettled and drier than average
OL,11,Fconditions. Although with outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain and stronger winds at times, more
OL,13,Fespecially across the north. There is
OL,14,Fstill a chance of some changeable or
OL,15,Fmore unsettled conditions developing
OL,16,Flater in the period, with a risk of
OL,17,Fsome heavy and thundery showers.
OL,18,FTemperatures are likely to be above
OL,19,Fnormal on the whole, with a greater
OL,20,Fthan normal chance of hot conditions
OL,21,Fdeveloping at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
